    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 specifies the regulatory standard condition and model influence is Medium. All three QoIs satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (percentage difference <10%, E/uval <1.96). Overall credibility is assessed as sufficient to support the Medium assurance level required for a Class II device submission.",
